{"tid":841884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麗港城商場對開有13枝支那五星國旗被噴上油漆及撕破","createTime":"2018-09-29T23:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T01:07:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":107,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1e2f1c0852bd4a26f85d0a49beca9bc743723e","tid":841884,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T23:15:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1420646-20180930.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1420646-20180930.htm&d=txGxP0W71hYQd4d9YDo6UghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=68bfa106\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1420646-20180930.htm&h=5f82b690\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1420646-20180930.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n觀塘茶果嶺道麗港城商場對開，發現有13枝國旗分別被人噴上油漆及撕破。<br />\n<br />\n警方於昨晚約10時半，接報有國旗被人損毀，警方追緝一名年約20至40歲瘦身材，案發時身穿深色上衣及深色短褲，戴黑色鴨舌帽男子。<br />\n<br />\n案件列作刑事毀壞。"},{"pid":"47270d83d99305a2c93fe7f8994878e0a01769e8","tid":841884,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T23:22:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6055f1d719cf282a5fb994e38dc2384dfd6c201","tid":841884,"uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T23:28:48.000Z","msg":"補返圖先, 有圖有真相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180929/large/1538233058_5162.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180929%2Flarge%2F1538233058_5162.jpg&h=c7a108c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23a26a0586f2004b936b2879c9f1e7b32b5b2e95","tid":841884,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T23:30:31.000Z","msg":"茶果嶺超過10支五星旗遭人淋黑油兼鎅爛！晚上7時許，有途人經過茶果嶺道時，發現多支掛在行人路的五星旗被淋上黑油及鎅爛，《蘋果》到場視察，發現麗港城商場對開一段茶果嶺道有4支五星旗被淋上黑油，1支五星旗被撕毀，而麗港城16座對開的一段茶果嶺道亦有4支五星旗遭鎅爛，4支五星旗遭淋黑。至晚上10時許，多名便衣探員及軍裝警先後到場調查。涉案男子年約20至40歲，瘦身材，案發時身穿深色上衣及深色短褲，戴黑色鴨舌帽。<br />\n<br />\n現場除了有五星旗外，亦有區旗及地區組織的旗幟，但未有被人弄污或毀壞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180929/large/1538233058_fd7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180929%2Flarge%2F1538233058_fd7c.jpg&h=f73719f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180929/large/1538233058_150c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180929%2Flarge%2F1538233058_150c.jpg&h=940551eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180929/large/1538233086_f24b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180929%2Flarge%2F1538233086_f24b.jpg&h=fb06af4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9724a4261ffcef8c1e530d6353ad1cc9bb641c58","tid":841884,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T23:33:17.000Z","msg":"坐監je,，冇咩大不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab5f15a804cdd7b5413cc90f5b18f973dd425d1","tid":841884,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"9724a4261ffcef8c1e530d6353ad1cc9bb641c58","tid":841884,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T23:33:17.000Z","msg":"坐監je,，冇咩大不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T23:37:21.000Z","msg":"捉唔到咪無事囉<br />\n<br />\n關健係手腳乾唔乾淨<br />\n<br />\n以前義士對保共街頭BANNER公開行刑, 咪一樣無事<br />\n<br />\n重點完全係乾淨脷落, 捉唔到"},{"pid":"dbb8f0784a129953fa1c06850db9ccee06b9f3ef","tid":841884,"uid":12021,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T00:00:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"030cd20451c24f1d6f1158dcd86dab901615fbde","tid":841884,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbb8f0784a129953fa1c06850db9ccee06b9f3ef","ti